1. New Trick action and Trick status
    * Trick n (action)
        - Gain n "Trick" cards.
    * Trick n (status)
        - Gain n "Trick" cards at start of your turn.
    * "Trick" cards
        - Veer
            * Move Right 2, flippable
        - Drift Left
            * Move Right 1, Move Left 2, Hermes 1
        - Drift Right
            * Move Left 1, Move Right 2, Hermes 1
        - Shake Left
            * Move Random 1, Move Left 2
        - Shake Right
            * Move Random 1, Move Right 2
        - Juke Left
            * Move Random 1, Move Random 2
        - Juke Right
            * Move Random 1, Move Random 2
        - Blink
            * Move Right 3, flippable
        - Flicker
            * Move Random 3
2. Fade nerfs
    * Proposed idea: Make Fade be set instead.
        - Prevents gaining a lot of Fade in a single turn.
        - Incentivizes using more expensive Fade cards (because you get more).